        <updateDate>2007-11-09T19:42:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Permanent Internet Tax Freedom Act of 2007 - Amends the Internet Tax Freedom Act to make permanent the ban on state and local taxation of Internet access and on multiple or discriminatory taxes on electronic commerce. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
